      "id": "PopularPost368640",
      "post_content": "@**dberry02**  \nNice try, but clashkill84 is right.  \n  \n@**clashkill84**  \nYou're not as right as you think you are. If you do as dberry suggests and [Mirrorweave](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mirrorweave) all creatures into Blacker Lotuses then all of your opponent's creatures will become 0/0s and die (yours won't because you have your [Tempered Steel](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Tempered Steel)) I'm sure there's ways of buffing your opponents creatures (maybe even with their own hand after your [Mindslaver](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mindslaver) is activated) and you'll likely still win the game after all this happens, but *who cares about winning* when you have a chance to **legally tear up your opponent's cards**?",
      "posted_by": "Crotchkicker",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost368640\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">@<b>dberry02</b><br/>Nice try, but clashkill84 is right.<br/><br/>@<b>clashkill84</b><br/>You're not as right as you think you are. If you do as dberry suggests and <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mirrorweave\">Mirrorweave</a> all creatures into Blacker Lotuses then <u>all of your opponent's creatures will become 0/0s and die</u> (yours won't because you have your <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Tempered Steel\">Tempered Steel</a>) I'm sure there's ways of buffing your opponents creatures (maybe even with their own hand after your <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mindslaver\">Mindslaver</a> is activated) and you'll likely still win the game after all this happens, but <i>who cares about winning</i> when you have a chance to<b> legally tear up your opponent's cards</b>?</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy76721\">Crotchkicker</span>\r\n                                (3/24/2014 12:55:54 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div